ss=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usoygen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Soygen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 11:06:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Valdanov Zevfeer quest question....</span><hr size=1> I'm assuming this quest is still unsolved?<br><br>Anyway, I'm at the point of handing the idol into Lathin Firetree, but before I do, what kind of group does this fight require? I don't want to get killed and end up having to start from scratch. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Thanks<br>Soy <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucelestin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Celestin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 12:19:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Valdanov Zevfeer quest question....</span><hr size=1> I was able to do this fight solo as a 60 shaman, but it was the toughest solo fight I've done in a LONG time.  (Well ok, nearly solo.  Thanks for the help at the end.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )  Recommend at least 3 folks with a slower if you're going to melee.  Root/park/dot works fine.  60 can single pull, if you can avoid the proximity agro.<br><br>Celestin<br>Oracle of Bertoxx <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usoygen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Soygen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 12:24:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Valdanov Zevfeer quest question....</span><hr size=1> I'm a 60 Monk and will probably have all 60's with me when I do this. Do the mobs immediately aggro when they are summoned or is there a delay? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upedriccuf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pedric Cuf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 3:33:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Valdanov Zevfeer quest question....</span><hr size=1> Ok, just did this myself. What happens is you hand the idol to the guy upstairs, then you run to the bottom floor and hand it to the head summoner. Then a shade lord will pop in the middle, but do not aggro. There will be a lot of dialogue, and then the head summoner will collapse. 3 more shades will spawn at the corners on both sides of the door when coming in, and at the top right corner. The Lord conned red to me at 49 and the normals were blue. The Lord will cast gate when low on HP and he is NOT interruptable, so the only way to kill him is to destroy him fast at that point or keep at him till he finally gets out of mana. Also, if dragged out, the lord will camp in one spot and not move. I did this with a group consisting of a 51 monk, 52 warrior, 52 cleric, 49 enchanter, and me, 49 rogue. But we didn't do it easily. <br><br>First time was a pull of the lord and two shades and we couldn't get past his gate, so the warrior and I died, but the rest reached safety. We reformed after we were routed and ended up taking them all down. Good luck to you, and make sure you loot all four robes.<br><br>Edit: Oh, to let you know, the shades are all necros so have MR, DR, and PR up. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upedriccuf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pedric Cuf</A> at: 3/11/02 3:34:58 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=thedunadain>The Dunadain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 5:41:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Autarkic Lord Sfarosh and Gang</span><hr size=1> This fight is horribly easy, for these mobs can be single pulled without the aid of a monk or harmo-type spells. Once you hand in the idol and stuff, get out of the building. Wait until you see that all of the summoners of the lord have despawned, and then carefully pull one or two shades at a time (we did lord last). I've done this 3 or 4 times, and each fight was a piece of cake.<br>   The groups were rather simple as well.. all but the lord were blue to a 49. The 1st time I did it I had a 50 druid, a 49 monk, and myself (47 pally). The 2nd time we had 3-5 lvl 50-55, and the 3rd time I helped a few people who were lvl 60, which isn't even worth mentioning... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usoygen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Soygen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/11/02 5:44:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Autarkic Lord Sfarosh and Gang</span><hr size=1> Man, this fight was easy. Kinda' makes me wonder what the final reward will be if ANYONE ever finds this bastage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usorinie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sorinie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/12/02 1:02:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Autarkic Lord Sfarosh and Gang</span><hr size=1> Yeah, I have been thinking about that.  The only difficult part of the quest is.. well.. it's all easy.. and easily doable by all but the crappiest equiped players.  How great can the reward actually be?  My guess is this.. It is set to be like the LSoEE was.  There will be an above average, yet far from uber item as reward.  This will last about.. Oh, 1 to 2 weeks. Then it will get hit with the nerf bat with all the verocity of machine gun toting monkies in a Tiffany's store.  My guess is 2 things.. one nerfable, the other not.  First guess is a spell or song.  I'm guessing other will be a Katta Castleium Badge of Service with stats... only makes sence. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udarjeeling.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darjeeling</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/12/02 1:33:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Autarkic Lord Sfarosh and Gang</span><hr size=1> When i did it, we got a double spawn. Eight mobs for our group of 4. We killed all 8, but i died and only got to loot one robe.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=4376.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4376.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4376.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4376.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This